title: President Obama to Deliver Commencement Addresses at Barnard College, Joplin High School and the Air Force Academy | whitehouse.gov
content:
The White House
Office of the Press Secretary


For Immediate Release
March 05, 2012

 



President Obama to Deliver Commencement Addresses at Barnard College, Joplin High School and the Air Force Academy





	WASHINGTON, DC â€“ President Obama will deliver three commencement addresses this spring at Barnard College in New York City on May 14, Joplin High School in Joplin, Missouri on May 21, and the Air Force Academy in Colorado Springs, Colorado on May 23.
